PCF Component Spec: FM Enhanced TextField
Overview
A bound field component for Single Line and Multiple Line text fields in Model-Driven Apps (Dynamics 365 / Dataverse). Shows a live character counter (used / max) and adds contextual icons and actions based on field type (Phone, Email, URL).
Namespace: Fellowmind
Component Name: FM Enhanced TextField
Framework: React (TSX) + Fluent UI v9 (@fluentui/react-components)

Why
Fields like invoice line descriptions often have a max length enforced by Dataverse. Users only discover the limit when they hit a validation error. This component shows remaining space in real time, preventing errors and improving the filling experience.

