Edge Cases to Handle

MaxLength = 0 or undefined — treat as unlimited, hide counter
Null value — treat as empty string, counter shows 0 / max
Paste event — if pasted text exceeds max, do NOT truncate automatically (let Dataverse handle validation), but show clear over-limit warning
IME input (CJK characters) — use onCompositionStart / onCompositionEnd to avoid updating during IME composition
Field security — if field is secured and user has no read access, value.raw may be null and value.security will indicate this. Show appropriate masked UI.
RTL support — counter and icon placement should respect context.userSettings.isRTL


